<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.2">
<l>aṉuṅka veṉṉaip pirivucey tāyar pāṭi kavarntuṇṇuṅ</l>
<l>kuṇuṅku nāṟik kuṭṭēṟṟaik kōvart taṉaṉaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>kaṇaṅka ḷōṭu miṉmēkaṅ kalantāṟ pōla, vaṉamālai</l>
<l>miṉuṅka niṉṟu viḷaiyāṭa viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see He who smells of cattle who eats by robbing Gokula,</l>
<l>Having parted from me so that [I] suffer pain, the Little Bull, the Cattle-Grower?</l>
<l>We saw Him play in Bṛndāvana so that [His] tulsi garland shone on,</l>
<l>As if seeing a [bolt of] lightning and a cloud that had merged, along with groups [of friends]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
